These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
Flower: marigold, amaryllis
1. Flower:amaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
2. Flower:marigold is on the right of Flower:amaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Flower   | amaryllis | marigold |

 #################################
 
